    <string name="about_company_description" translatable="false">The OpenWeb Sample App is a live showcase of our SDK capabilities and recommended implementation patterns.\n\nIt features production-ready examples of OpenWeb\'s engagement experiences - including pre-conversation units, full conversations, side-rail placements, and video integrations across multiple content verticals such as news, finance, sports, recipes, and more.\n\nDesigned as both a demonstration environment and a best-practice reference, the app highlights the flexibility, performance, and adaptability of the OpenWeb platform, helping partners better understand how our solutions can be integrated into their own products.</string>
